Rules for Participation. The document contained the following specific instructions to participants:
a. b.
Add your name to the roster so that the next person who receives this folder will know whom it came from.
Detach one postcard from the bottom of this folder. Fill it out and return it to Harvard University. No stamp is needed. The postcard is very important. It allows us to keep track of the progress of the folder as it moves toward the target person.
